        <item>
            <title><![CDATA[【[并不简单]#近视超过多少度应该戴眼镜#】今年3月，是第8个全国近视防控宣传教育月。医生表示，#戴眼镜会让视力变差是错误认知#，如果近视度数到达或超过100度...]]></title>
            <description><![CDATA[【<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[并不简单]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/d_bingbujiandan-9955880b30.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E8%BF%91%E8%A7%86%E8%B6%85%E8%BF%87%E5%A4%9A%E5%B0%91%E5%BA%A6%E5%BA%94%E8%AF%A5%E6%88%B4%E7%9C%BC%E9%95%9C%23&amp;extparam=%23%E8%BF%91%E8%A7%86%E8%B6%85%E8%BF%87%E5%A4%9A%E5%B0%91%E5%BA%A6%E5%BA%94%E8%AF%A5%E6%88%B4%E7%9C%BC%E9%95%9C%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#近视超过多少度应该戴眼镜#</span></a>】今年3月，是第8个全国近视防控宣传教育月。医生表示，<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E6%88%B4%E7%9C%BC%E9%95%9C%E4%BC%9A%E8%AE%A9%E8%A7%86%E5%8A%9B%E5%8F%98%E5%B7%AE%E6%98%AF%E9%94%99%E8%AF%AF%E8%AE%A4%E7%9F%A5%23&amp;extparam=%23%E6%88%B4%E7%9C%BC%E9%95%9C%E4%BC%9A%E8%AE%A9%E8%A7%86%E5%8A%9B%E5%8F%98%E5%B7%AE%E6%98%AF%E9%94%99%E8%AF%AF%E8%AE%A4%E7%9F%A5%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#戴眼镜会让视力变差是错误认知#</span></a>，如果近视度数到达或超过100度，导致远视力明显下降、学习生活受影响时，就应当配戴眼镜👇🏻（央视新闻） <a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034:5012127853772855" data-hide=""><span class="url-icon"><img style="width: 1rem;height: 1rem" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/upload/2015/09/25/3/timeline_card_small_video_default.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><span class="surl-text">人民日报的微博视频</span></a> <br clear="both"><div style="clear: both"></div><video controls="controls" poster="https://tvax1.sinaimg.cn/orj480/0033ImPzly1hnrg1oqrdkj61hc0u0tfi02.jpg" style="width: 100%"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/J9iAZ53plx08diyhi4y401041200uyts0E010.mp4?label=mp4_720p&amp;template=1280x720.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1710608550&amp;ssig=oNEgXp16TL&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/XUKRWoWmlx08diyg7hKg01041200gfHU0E010.mp4?label=mp4_hd&amp;template=852x480.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1710608550&amp;ssig=HIk1lw5%2Fla&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/JTeN4x2clx08diyfAQoU01041200abzQ0E010.mp4?label=mp4_ld&amp;template=640x360.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1710608550&amp;ssig=7b9KLkvYc9&amp;KID=unistore,video"><p>视频无法显示，请前往<a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034%3A5012127853772855" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">微博视频</a>观看。</p></video>]]></description>
