        <item>
            <title><![CDATA[【[奥特曼]#预防流行性腮腺炎的4个方法#】流行性腮腺炎简称流腮，俗称“痄腮”，被我国列为法定的丙类传染病。#腮腺肿大不一定是得了流行性腮腺炎#，还有很多疾...]]></title>
            <description><![CDATA[【<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[奥特曼]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/others/d_aoteman-7ddbc90d1c.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E9%A2%84%E9%98%B2%E6%B5%81%E8%A1%8C%E6%80%A7%E8%85%AE%E8%85%BA%E7%82%8E%E7%9A%844%E4%B8%AA%E6%96%B9%E6%B3%95%23&amp;extparam=%23%E9%A2%84%E9%98%B2%E6%B5%81%E8%A1%8C%E6%80%A7%E8%85%AE%E8%85%BA%E7%82%8E%E7%9A%844%E4%B8%AA%E6%96%B9%E6%B3%95%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#预防流行性腮腺炎的4个方法#</span></a>】流行性腮腺炎简称流腮，俗称“痄腮”，被我国列为法定的丙类传染病。<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E8%85%AE%E8%85%BA%E8%82%BF%E5%A4%A7%E4%B8%8D%E4%B8%80%E5%AE%9A%E6%98%AF%E5%BE%97%E4%BA%86%E6%B5%81%E8%A1%8C%E6%80%A7%E8%85%AE%E8%85%BA%E7%82%8E%23&amp;extparam=%23%E8%85%AE%E8%85%BA%E8%82%BF%E5%A4%A7%E4%B8%8D%E4%B8%80%E5%AE%9A%E6%98%AF%E5%BE%97%E4%BA%86%E6%B5%81%E8%A1%8C%E6%80%A7%E8%85%AE%E8%85%BA%E7%82%8E%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#腮腺肿大不一定是得了流行性腮腺炎#</span></a>，还有很多疾病能引起腮腺肿大。当发生腮腺肿大时，建议及时就诊。医生建议：①每天开窗通风半个小时以上，保证空气的清新；②保持良好的个人卫生习惯；③免疫力差的人外出时需要戴口罩；④避免过度疲劳、保证睡眠质量、加强体育锻炼等，提高自身免疫力<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[加油]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/d_jiayou-a34ced0409.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>（央视网）<a href="http://t.cn/A6YkFxUL" data-hide=""><span class="url-icon"><img style="width: 1rem;height: 1rem" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/upload/2015/09/25/3/timeline_card_small_web_default.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span> <span class="surl-text">网页链接</span></a>]]></description>
