        <item>
            <title><![CDATA[[哆啦A梦害怕]#叉腿坐比并腿坐更健康吗#？网上说，叉开腿坐才是最健康的坐姿，真的假的？这种说法还有待商榷🙋🏻♂️。正确坐姿是大腿与座椅平齐或稍低于座...]]></title>
            <description><![CDATA[<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[哆啦A梦害怕]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/doraemon/dr_03haipa-32e9b53caf.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%8F%89%E8%85%BF%E5%9D%90%E6%AF%94%E5%B9%B6%E8%85%BF%E5%9D%90%E6%9B%B4%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%E5%90%97%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%8F%89%E8%85%BF%E5%9D%90%E6%AF%94%E5%B9%B6%E8%85%BF%E5%9D%90%E6%9B%B4%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%E5%90%97%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#叉腿坐比并腿坐更健康吗#</span></a>？网上说，叉开腿坐才是最健康的坐姿，真的假的？<br><br>这种说法还有待商榷🙋🏻♂️。正确坐姿是大腿与座椅平齐或稍低于座椅，双脚平放在地面上，脊椎在自然状态下竖直两肩水平，头微向前倾。这种坐姿能让头和脊柱保持正确的曲线，骨盆中立胸部敞开，可以维持肺部充足的通气量。<br><br>和卫一起看看搬砖人错误的坐姿有哪些？哪一款才是正确坐姿？<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[开学季]" src="https://face.t.sinajs.cn/t4/appstyle/expression/ext/normal/72/2021_kaixueji_org.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>👇🏻<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#小卫唠健康#</span></a><a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E6%9D%A5%E8%BE%9F%E8%B0%A3%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E6%9D%A5%E8%BE%9F%E8%B0%A3%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#小卫来辟谣#</span></a>（健康中国）<br><br>你们搬砖时都是什么坐姿<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[doge]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/others/d_doge-be7f768d78.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span> <br><br>（除了正确坐姿，前面的都是卫的日常坐姿<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[跪了]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/d_guile-a8a737d3a0.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><img style="" src="https://tvax3.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hnriph84iqj20u0143jtw.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://tvax1.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hnripgl675j20u0143go2.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://tvax3.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hnriph7iy1j20u0143q5u.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://tvax1.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hnripgup89j20u01430vj.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://tvax2.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hnripgr8tpj20u0143tbh.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://tvax4.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hnripgj42vj20u0143act.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://tvax3.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hnripgd7wmj20u0143mzr.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br>]]></description>
